    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我理解是要从车队管理模块开始。不过您提到\"连到运单号那边\"，是指直接从FleetManagement跳到TrackingNumber，还是中间需要经过一个环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间应该还有一个FleetManagement节点，表示调度分配后的状态。所以结构是：FleetManagement起点 → 另一个FleetManagement节点 → 最后到TrackingNumber。这样体现状态变更。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解是三个节点：第一个FleetManagement作为入口，第二个FleetManagement表示调度后状态，最后TrackingNumber作为追踪输出。两条箭头都是单向流向，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，方向别搞反了，从上到下或者从左到右都可以，但要清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，用TB方向布局，三个节点依次连接。您看一下这个结构是否符合预期？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "方向没问题，但我发现第二个节点和第三个节点的标签好像有点混淆——第二个应该是FleetManagement，第三个是TrackingNumber，确认一下标签没贴错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
