      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "确认无误，已修正：A是FleetManagement起点，B是调度后的FleetManagement，C是TrackingNumber。标签和流向都正确了。",
